{"TopicId":205947,"ForumId":36,"TopicTitle":"How do you make mods?","CreatedByName":"Zeldagamer809","CreatedById":217808,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-12-12T01:58:13Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Zeldagamer809","CreatedById":217808,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-12-12T01:58:13Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI don\u0027t really know how to make a custom mod, so I am wondering where I can make a custom mod without downloading a lot of stuff.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"HebaruSan","CreatedById":156657,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-12-12T03:33:56Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThis is a decent place to start:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022\u0022 data-controller=\u0022core.front.core.autosizeiframe\u0022 data-embedauthorid=\u002262955\u0022 data-embedcontent=\u0022\u0022 data-embedid=\u0022embed6132450509\u0022 scrolling=\u0022no\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/170231-useful-references-for-modding-all-the-old-stickies/\u0026amp;do=embed\u0022 style=\u0022height:198px;max-width:502px;\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Vanamonde","CreatedById":27914,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-12-12T04:17:34Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI have not made any myself but I have moved your question to the place where others have and may be able to help. Good luck. \u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u00A0\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Lisias","CreatedById":187168,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-12-12T13:47:14Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224064301\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022205947\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221639274293\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022217808\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Zeldagamer809\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n11 hours ago, Zeldagamer809 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI don\u0027t really know how to make a custom mod, so I am wondering where I can make a custom mod without downloading a lot of stuff.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThere\u0027re really many different ways, it will depend on what you are planning to do.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cul\u003E\u003Cli\u003E\nYou want change something on the game mechanics (like SystemHeat)?\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nDo you want to add some visuals (like Distant Object)?\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nDo you want to make a new Planet or perhaps a whole Solar System?\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nPlan to create new parts?\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nOr perhaps just change some of them?\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nWant some new convenience\u00A0 utility like UbioWelding?\u00A0\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nPerhaps new buildings or launching places around Kerbin (and beyound)?\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003C/ul\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\nYou see, depending from what you want to do, you will have to learn different things.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSome of then are common to all options, as writing configs and patches.\u00A0 But some others are pretty task specific.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nLet us know what you intend to do.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222021-12-12T13:49:01Z\u0022 title=\u002212/12/2021 01:49  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00222 yr\u0022\u003EDecember 12, 2021\u003C/time\u003E by Lisias\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003Cbr\u003EBetter formatting\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Gargamel","CreatedById":64714,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-12-12T15:17:59Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMoved to Add-on Developement.\u00A0 \u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:D\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:D\u0022\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}